24 SECTION 4. GRANTS, GIFTS, AND DONATIONS LINE ITEM. The grants, gifts, and
25 donations line item in section 1 of this Act includes up to $100,000 received by the game and
26 fish department for surface damage, easements, or reclamation on department-owned or
27 managed properties as a result of mineral exploration and extraction activities.
28 SECTION 5. MIDTERM CONSERVATION AGREEMENTS. The game and fish department
29 may spend up to $2,777,778 from other funds in the land habitat and deer depredation line item
30 in section 1 of this Act for national fish and wildlife foundation midterm conservation agreements
31 with private landowners. The department shall limit the term of these agreements to a maximum
